## Detection
| Source | Event ID | Indicator |
|---|---|---|
| Windows Security Log | 4769 | RC4 encryption (0x17) TGS request |
| Wazuh | Rule 100010 | Kerberoasting — T1558.003 |

## Remediation
- Migrate service accounts to gMSA
- Enforce AES-only Kerberos encryption
- Use passwords longer than 25 characters for service accounts
